high_descs: turn and walk to the left so you see the stove and, knife and potato on the counter top
pick up the knife from the counter top
turn and walk to the right while holding the knife until you face the counter top with the toaster on it
slice the potato on this counter top into thin slices with the knife
turn to the right completely while holding the knife
find and open the black cabinet underneath the counter top slightly left of the sink.
open the cabinet and place the knife into the white shelf inside the cabinet
turn to the right and go to the counter top with the sliced potato
pick up a slice of the potato
turn to the right and face the sink and wash the potato slice in the sink under the faucet
turn right and walk toward the microwave oven
place the potato slice on the counter in front of the microwave
anns.task_desc: Take a knife, slice a potato, wash a slice, place it on the counter in front of the microwave oven.

high_descs: Walk towards the sink, turn right then walk towards the stove.
Pick up the knife that is located on the right side of the stove.
Turn right towards the potato on the counter nearest the toaster
Cut the potato, near the toaster, into slices.
Turn right then walk toward the sink, turn right and walk towards the table, then turn all the way around and face the sink
Open the cabinet door underneath the counter top on the left side and place the knife on the shelf.
Turn left then walk towards the stove, then turn right and walk towards the counter top.
Pick up a slice of potato from the counter top.
Take the potato slice and turn right, then turn left in front of the sink.
Place the potato slice in the sink, in front of the tomato, then turn the water on, rinse the potato slice, then turn the water off.
Pick up the potato slice, turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right again and walk towards the microwave.
Place the potato slice on the left side of the table in front of the pepper shaker.
anns.task_desc: Cut a potato into slices placing it in front of the pepper shaker.

high_descs: Turn left and head to the counter
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn right and face the counter in front of you
Cut the potato into slices
Back up from the counter
Open the left cabinet below the counter and put the knife inside. Close the cabinet.
Walk up to the counter in front of you
Grab one of the potato slices
Turn right and head to the sink
Wash the potato in the sink and then take it out
Turn around and head to the microwave
Place the potato down on the black table
anns.task_desc: Putting a potato slice on the black table

high_descs: Turn left and head to the counter to the left of the stove
Grab the knife off of the counter
Turn to your right and face the counter
Cut the potato into slices
Back up from the counter
Open the lower left cabinet on the bottom and put the knife inside
Go straight to the counter
Grab a slice of the potato
Turn right and stop at the sink
Wash the potato in the sink and take it out
Turn around and head to the microwave
Put the potato on the black table
anns.task_desc: Putting a potato slice on the black table

high_descs: Go to the counter on your left.
Take the knife you see on the counter.
Turn to your right.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Back away from the counter.
Place the knife in the cabinet under the counter.
Turn back to the potato you just cut.
Take a slice of the potato.
Turn right, walk to the sink, then turn left to face the sink.
Wash the slice of potato in the sink.
Go to the microwave cart behind you.
Place the slice of potato on the microwave cart.
anns.task_desc: Prepare a potato to cook in the microwave without leaving dirty dishes out.
